===to check the usage of the  cpu 
sudo mpstat  -u -P 0,1,2,3 1

===to check the interupts per cpu

sudo mpstat -I SUM -P 0,1,2,3 1

=== to check the both things 

sudo mpstat -u -I SUM -P 0,1,2,3 1

<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<< How to connect with rempte pc under same network >>>>>>>>>>>>>>>>
--> install open ssh on the server == sudo apt-get install opensssh-server
--> start ssh server at host == sudo service ssh start
--> check the status at host == sudo service ssh status

from client

--- simply run the command---> ssh <<server_pc username>>@<<server ip>> 
---- enter the password << server loginpassword>>
